{"tid":2263864,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"邱騰華：正式要求世貿處理對美投訴 限10日內回應 30日內坐底傾 否則申請仲裁","createTime":"2020-10-30T08:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T02:06:33.000Z","uid":21470,"like":75,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":131,"replies":[{"pid":"9134c40057cd38656f0c7d34aab22183292dbb11","tid":2263864,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:05:55.000Z","msg":"就港貨來源標記 邱騰華稱正式要求世貿處理對美投訴<br />\n<br />\n特區政府因應本港輸往美國貨品，產地來源標記要改為「中國製造」的新規定，今日根據世界貿易組織爭端解決機制，正式啟動程序，要求世貿處理香港對美國的投訴。<br />\n<br />\n香港特區駐世貿常設代表，已經向美國駐世貿代表發出通知，要求美方就新規定進行磋商。<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華會見傳媒時表示，美方過往6星期的反應令人失望，香港有必要向美方採取進一步行動。根據世貿機制，美方需要在特區政府提出磋商後，10日內作出回應，亦要在30日內與香港進行磋商。<br />\n<br />\n如果雙方未能在60日內透過磋商得到解決，特區政府有權、亦會要求世貿設立專家小組，審議有關爭端。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557484-20201030.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557484-20201030.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KPhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=84ad0d73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557484-20201030.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c6119c06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557484-20201030.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"0f99827a01495ad48f8d47b942724aedffc154c5","tid":2263864,"uid":33263,"like":142,"dislike":1,"score":141,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:07:04.000Z","msg":"美國都差唔多退出WTO<br />\n你仲裁有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3706f764f5fef178643506960c6454c8756ec34","tid":2263864,"uid":11454,"like":80,"dislike":0,"score":80,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:07:33.000Z","msg":"同時間， 支那安插尼日利亞入WTO做主席<br />\n可惜俾美國一票反對左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6a5e34f4e2a55c74df6f5bd35a4a21615fe789","tid":2263864,"uid":66324,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"0f9